originalText.text: They ransacked my car and stole $40 and all my quarters.  If you're going to steal things from my car at least be professional enough to put everything else back how you found it.

originalText.text: DONT EVER COME HERE!!!!!!!!! YOU MIGHT REGRET IT!!!! I REPEAT...DONT!!!!! If could post with no stars I would!!! I work at the hospital nearby. I parked here today at around 7AM after getting up late this morning. Reservations were made with spothero. I had used this place on a few occasions when it was convenient and didnt think anything of it. This spot is known for their daily early bird rates. $160 that was placed in the center console of the car (Mercedes C300) in a compartment near by the cup holders the day before. I was going to use the money to pay back my mother. I left it there and only remembered about it when I was halfway to work. I got back to the car around 8:00PM and as I got my car i was getting settled when the valet drove behind and honked me out the way so I drove off. When i got home I searched for the money and could not find it. I called them and a man picked up and claim he did not speak English and that I would have to call back in the morning for someone who did and hung up and did not pick up any further calls. I called spothero (according to their policy they are not responsible) and they tried to call, only to have them hang up without speaking to them about they heard the issue. You pay for service not thinking that your privacy and belongs would be violated. You entrust your hard earned investment....this is not what you expect. I will have to call the police in the AM.

Terrible service. I was waiting for my car and the manager told me to me I said I am waiting for my car, he then said I have a new customer can you move.

It wasn't busy he had no need to talk to me the way he did. A simple excuse me sir can you please step to the side so I can attend to the never customer but not once but twice but three times. MOVE   MOVE OVER THERE
